Ebbro 44768 Nissan Skyline GT-R 1996 Sendai Hi-Land (JGTC Round 3) 5th Place M. Kageyama/K. Hoshino

Manufacturer page: http://ebbro.co.jp/item_japangp/4427312112231111111131111.html

Masahiko Kageyama & Kazuyoshi Hoshino drove this Skyline in round 4 of the 1996 JGTC Series - Sendai Hi-Land. They qualified in 10th place and went on to finish the race in 5th place.
